## Minimal tooling additions (consistent with stack)

Add to **`devDependencies`** (versions pinned per team policy):

- **`vitest`**, **`@vitejs/plugin-react`** (or Vitest’s documented Next.js/React setup), **`jsdom`**, **`@testing-library/react`**, **`@testing-library/jest-dom`**, **`@testing-library/user-event`** — for unit/component tests per **`vitest-testing.mdc`**.
- **`@playwright/test`** — for browser E2E against **`next dev`**, **`next start`**, or **`opennextjs-cloudflare preview`** as chosen target.

Suggested **`package.json` scripts:**

- `"test": "vitest"` — unit/component (CI: `vitest run`).
- `"test:e2e": "playwright test"` — E2E (CI: same, headless).
- Optional: `"test:e2e:ui": "playwright test --ui"` for local debugging.

