## Sprint 1 completion checklist (all phases)

Run before marking Sprint 1 auth **done**:

### Environment & CI

- [ ] `PLAYWRIGHT_BASE_URL` documented; CI installs browsers and runs **headless** E2E green.
- [ ] Local D1 reset documented; developers can run E2E twice in a row without manual DB surgery.

### Auth flows (automated)

- [ ] Signup success; duplicate email error path.
- [ ] Login success; bad password.
- [ ] `/me` with valid Bearer token; `/me` without token (401 or equivalent).
- [ ] Logout clears **`quizmaker_auth_token`** and lands on agreed public route (**signup or login** per product).

### Cross-cutting

- [ ] Wrong base URL / unreachable server causes **obvious** failure (not a false green).
- [ ] **CORS / origin** documented for `next dev` and optional Worker **preview**; E2E config matches.

### Quality bar

- [ ] No placeholder tests (`expect(true).toBe(true)`) per **`vitest-testing.mdc`** for any added unit tests.
- [ ] Passwords and JWTs not printed in CI logs.

